text.tspan: Digital Culture lectures at Escola Viva - Vila Olmpia, So Paulo
Extracurricular classes for teenagers during 3 semesters covering Digital Culture topics such as:
* Copyright Law and free licenses such as the GNU GPL and the licenses of the Creative Commons project.
* GNU/Linux and the history if the Free Software movement.
* Digital Fabrication techniques (overview of 3d printers, laser cutters and other CNC machines)
